update and fix the notebooks (#28)

* updated notebooks to work with newest version of numpy and with ehrdata obejcts

changed np.NaN to np.nan
changed type_overview to feature_type_overview
converted anndata objects to ehrdata

* reduced dataset to first 1000 items before imputation due to long imputation time

* removed last umap steps due to labels not existing anymore

* fixed download of thyroid data to work with new location of files. modified files location in gitignore

* removed mimic3 preprocessing as it is no longer needed

* updated run_notebooks.yml to install ehrdata package

* fixed metadata of all notebooks to run with CI

* fixed patoolib import

* updated gitignore to include .rar files

* removed tracked rar file

* added parkinson's_disease_classification to notebook matrix and ordered items in matrix alphabetically

* removed apostrophe in directory and file names and cleaned up unnecessary outputs
